Up Close and Personal	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BuccaneerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Buccaneers are skilled at the close quarter fighting involved in all boarding actions. When fighting with two small size weapons, the penalties for fighting with two weapons is reduced by a further -2 as soon as the buccaneer achieve the 2nd level.	KEY:Buccaneer ~ Up Close and Personal									BONUS:COMBAT|TOHIT-PRIMARY|2|PREMULT:2,[PREEQUIPPRIMARY:1,WIELDCATEGORY=Light],[PREEQUIPSECONDARY:1,WIELDCATEGORY=Light]	BONUS:COMBAT|TOHIT-SECONDARY|2|PREMULT:2,[PREEQUIPPRIMARY:1,WIELDCATEGORY=Light],[PREEQUIPSECONDARY:1,WIELDCATEGORY=Light]																SORTKEY:Class_Buccaneer	SOURCEPAGE:SoB
Witty Repartee	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BuccaneerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When engaged in melee combat, the buccaneer keeps up a steady stream of banter that can soon infuriate an unbalanced opponent. From 3rd level onwards, the buccaneer may use hi witty repartee class feature in conjunction with a full attack combat option. Both he and one opponent make a opposed Will checks, with the buccaneers using his class level as a bonus modifier (+%1 bonus). If the buccaneer is successful, his opponent suffers a -2 morale penalty to all attacks rolls until the start of the buccaneer's next round.|WittyReparteeBonus	KEY:Buccaneer ~ Witty Repartee				DEFINE:WittyReparteeBonus|0					BONUS:VAR|WittyReparteeBonus|BuccaneerLVL																	SORTKEY:Class_Buccaneer	SOURCEPAGE:SoB
Superb Seaman	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BuccaneerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:At 4th level, the buccaneer becomes so in tune with his ship and the sea that he may add a +2 competence bonus on all Seamanship checks. At 8th level, he receive a further +2 competence bonus on all Seamanship checks.	KEY:Buccaneer ~ Superb Seaman				DEFINE:SuperbSeamanBonus|0					BONUS:SKILL|Knowledge (Seamanship)|SuperbSeamanBonus|TYPE=Competence	BONUS:VAR|SuperbSeamanBonus|2|PREVARGTEQ:BuccaneerLVL,4	BONUS:VAR|SuperbSeamanBonus|2|PREVARGTEQ:BuccaneerLVL,8															SORTKEY:Class_Buccaneer	SOURCEPAGE:SoB
Swarm Rigging	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BuccaneerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The buccaneer can climb rigging and other ropes at his full movement rate at 5th level, as a move-equivalent action.	KEY:Buccaneer ~ Swarm Rigging																										SORTKEY:Class_Buccaneer	SOURCEPAGE:SoB
Superb Balance	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BuccaneerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Upon reaching 6th level, a buccaneer making a successful Balance check may move at full speed along any precarious surface.	KEY:Buccaneer ~ Superb Balance																										SORTKEY:Class_Buccaneer	SOURCEPAGE:SoB
Rope Fighting	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BuccaneerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:At 7th level, a buccaneer has become so proficient at fighting along masts and in the rigging that he may retain his dexterity bonus to his AC when engaged in combat. In addition enemies gain no bonus to hit when he is in such a position. The buccaneer will still lose his DEX bonus in other circumstances, such as being flat footed.	KEY:Buccaneer ~ Rope Fighting																										SORTKEY:Class_Buccaneer	SOURCEPAGE:SoB
Sabotage	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BuccaneerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Given 1d6 minutes, a 9th level buccaneer may sabotage a ship's rudder or rigging, halving its base speed and giving the ship a -2 circumstance penalty to its maneuverability. The sabotage may be rectified by the ship's crew with a seamanship check at DC 20. This will take one hour to complete.	KEY:Buccaneer ~ Sabotage																										SORTKEY:Class_Buccaneer	SOURCEPAGE:SoB
Acrobatic Defence	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.BuccaneerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:At 10th level, so long as he wears light or no armor and is not encumbered, the buccaneer gains +4 dodge AC bonus when executing the fight defensively standard or full round action. In addition he gains a +8 dodge AC bonus when executing the total defence standard action.	KEY:Buccaneer ~ Acrobatic Defence									BONUS:VAR|FightingDefensivelyACBonus|4|TYPE=Dodge|PREVARLT:ENCUMBERANCE,2,var("COUNT[EQTYPE.ARMOR.IS.HEAVY]"),1	BONUS:VAR|TotalDefenseACBonus|8|TYPE=Dodge|PREVARLT:ENCUMBERANCE,2,var("COUNT[EQTYPE.ARMOR.IS.HEAVY]"),1																SORTKEY:Class_Buccaneer	SOURCEPAGE:SoB
