Infallible Direction	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.NavigatorWizardClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:A Navigator-Wizard automatically knows where true north lies. This grants a +2 competence bonus to all Navigation checks.	KEY:Navigator Wizard ~ Infallible Direction									BONUS:SKILL|Knowledge (Seamanship)|2|TYPE=Competence	BONUS:SKILL|Profession (Navigator)|2|TYPE=Competence																SORTKEY:Class_Navigator_Wizard	SOURCEPAGE:SoB
Fast Pursuit	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.NavigatorWizardClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:At 2nd level navigator-wizard learns to maneuvre his ship to take best advantage of wind and wave to gain an advantage over any other vessel he is pursuing or trying to escape from. He may add his class level to nay opposed Seamanship checks made when involved in a pursuit, as detailed on p.22.	KEY:Navigator Wizard ~ Fast Pursuit																										SORTKEY:Class_Navigator_Wizard	SOURCEPAGE:SoB
Intuitive Seamanship	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.NavigatorWizardClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:At 3rd level, a navigator-wizard learns how to get the very best out of his ship and his crew. All seamanship checks made by the navigator-wizard or his crew receive a +2 competence bonus. At 6th and 9th this bonus rises to +4 and +6 respectively.	KEY:Navigator Wizard ~ Intuitive Seamanship				DEFINE:IntuitiveSeamanshipBonus|0					BONUS:VAR|IntuitiveSeamanshipBonus|(NavigatorWizardLVL/3)*2|TYPE=Competence																	SORTKEY:Class_Navigator_Wizard	SOURCEPAGE:SoB
Catch the Wind	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.NavigatorWizardClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:On achieving 4th level, the navigator-wizard is able to maneuvre his ship to take best advantage of winds and currents for sustained periods of time and may freely cast minor incantation to influence them. Any ship with a navigator-wizard on board may increase both his base and daily movement by 10%%.	KEY:Navigator Wizard ~ Catch the Wind																										SORTKEY:Class_Navigator_Wizard	SOURCEPAGE:SoB
